# vf-clamp-cli demo — Charmbracelet VHS. Render: vhs demo.tape -> assets/demo.gif
Output assets/demo.gif
Set FontSize 22
Set Width 1180
Set Height 660
Set Padding 26
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 55ms
Type "vf-clamp instances MyFont.ttf"
Enter
Sleep 18s
Type "vf-clamp clamp MyFont.ttf -i Regular -i Bold -n Text -f woff2"
Enter
Sleep 18s
Sleep 1s
